A man in a beige suit standing in front of a futuristic AI hair cutting machine. The sequence unfolds:

He takes a confident step forward toward the cylindrical pod machine with glowing blue circular opening. He leans his head forward, moving closer to the blue-lit portal. The camera follows smoothly as his head enters the opening. His current hairstyle remains completely unchanged during the approach and entry. Quick flashes of blue scanning lights sweep across his hair while inside. Holographic interface elements appear briefly - digital measurements, style selection icons. Only after the scanning completes, his hair transforms to a fresh new hairstyle (modern textured cut, neatly styled). He pulls back out of the machine with the new haircut. He runs his hand through his newly styled hair with a satisfied smile, nodding approvingly.

Camera: Smooth forward push, slight slow-motion on the reveal. Lighting: Modern showroom with blue LED accents.